Trademark and Copyright Notice

The name of this library (**ciri-navmesh**) is a reference to the character
Ciri (Cirilla) from "The Witcher" universe, originally created by Andrzej Sapkowski
and further popularized by CD Projekt Red.

This project is non-commercial, open-source, and distributed under the MIT License.
The author is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to the copyright holders
or trademark owners in any way. No financial gain or commercial benefit is intended.
The name is used solely as a tribute to the character and the incredible
work of her creators.
